@startuml

actor User

User -> Component: Interacts with UI
Component -> Selector: Selects state from store
Selector -> Component: Returns selected state
User -> Component: Triggers an action
Component -> Store: Dispatches the action
Store -> Reducer: Passes action and current state
Reducer -> Store: Returns new state
Store -> Component: Updates state
Component -> User: Renders updated UI

@enduml
